   <p><placeName ref="cwgk:P00000889">Fulton C<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">o</hi></hi></placeName> <date when="1864-01-11">Jan 11<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1864</date>
<lb/>To His Excellency
<lb/>Hon<persName ref="cwgk:N001000"> Tho<hi rend="sup">s</hi> E Bramlette</persName>,
<lb/>Governor of <orgName ref="cwgk:O001025">Ky</orgName>,
<lb/>D<hi rend="sup">r </hi>Sir,</p>
<p>Your Excellency's commission appointing me Major of the 3<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Bat,' <orgName ref="cwgk:O00000892">40<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Regt,' Ky Militia</orgName> is just received, I beg leave to Say, that I was elected to the position, without having been consulted on the Subject, and possessing no fitness for the place, I am unwilling to do violence to your generous confidence by rendering myself rediculous therein, I therefore respectfully decline the proffered honor.</p>
<p>Truly Your Ob<hi rend="sup">t</hi>' Serv<hi rend="sup">t</hi>'
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00000929">Ward Boyd</persName>.<pb/></p>
<p>Fulton Co <date when="1864-01-11">Jany 11<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> 1864</date><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Ward Boyd declines Comssion as Maj 3<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">rd</hi></hi> Bat 40<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> Regt Enrolled Militia<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Commission canceled and <persName ref="cwgk:N00000888">Col Hallet</persName> notified <date when="1864-01-30">Jany 30<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> 1864</date></p>
<p><hi rend="underline">see letter book</hi><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Rec<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> <orgName ref="cwgk:O00000920">I. G. O</orgName>. <date when="1864-01-29">Jany 29<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> 1864</date></p>
  </body>
